            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-100 mb-3 group-hover:text-emerald-700 dark:group-hover:text-emerald-300 transition-colors duration-300">Testing & Validation</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-sm mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Comprehensive testing, validation, and regulatory compliance.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400">
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-emerald-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Design verification and validation</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-emerald-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Regulatory documentation</li>
              <li class="flex items-center"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-emerald-400 rounded-full mr-2 group-hover:bg-emerald-500 transition-colors duration-300"></span>Compliance testing protocols</li>
